Odaily Planet Daily News According to Onchain Lens monitoring, in the past 6 hours: 
- Tether minted $1 billion USDT on the Tron network, and a total of $2 billion USDT has been minted so far in 2025; 
- Circle minted $250 million USDC on Solana, and a total of $6.5 billion USDC has been minted on Solana so far in 2025.
